---
import { ACTION_ERROR_CODES } from "astro:actions";
---

<section id="intro">
    <div class="intro-one">
        <p class="name">Hey y'all, my name is<span>Andrew Weisbeck</span></p>
        <h2 class="intro-desc">With over four years of experience as a freelance full-stack developer, I love to write clean code, create user-friendly apps, and design tech products for small businesses and non-profits.
        <br>
        <br> 
        I am currently seeking to grow in my career by exploring full-time opportunities with an organization where mentorship is available, teamwork and communication are valued, and quality of work is non-negotiable.</h2>
        <div class="btn-div">
            <a href="https://andrewweisbeck.com" class="buttonone" target="_blank">Get Resume</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="contact-btn" target="_blank">Contact Me</a>
        </div>
        
    </div>
    <div class="intro-grid">
        <div class="intro-two">
            <h3>Social Media and Content Sites</h3>
            <div class="site-pages">
                <a href="/about" class="about-btn">About Page</a>
                <a href="/portfolio" class="portfolio-btn">Portfolio Page</a>
                <a href="/blog" class="buttonone" target="_blank">Blog Page</a>
                <a href="/links" class="link-btn" target="_blank">Links Page</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="contact-btn" target="_blank">Contact Page</a>
            </div>
            
        </div>
        <div class="intro-three">
            <h3>How You Can Hire Me and Other External Sites</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://andrewweisbeck.com" class="buttontwo" target="_blank">Resume Website</a>: View my interactive resume and download a PDF version.</li>
                <li><p class="intro-text"><a href="https://tarheeldevstudio.com" class="buttonthree" target="_blank">Tar Heel Dev Studio</a></li>
                <li><p class="intro-text"><p class="intro-text">Don't hesitate to <a href="/contact" class="contact-btn" target="_blank">Contact Me</a> if you have a job opportunity or would like to collaborate on a project or idea - I'm always open to try something new!</p></li>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<style>
#intro {
    padding: 2rem 4rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

#intro p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-family: var(--mono);
}

#intro img {
    padding: 0;
}

#intro h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--white);
}

#intro .name {
    margin: 1rem auto;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--white);
}

.name span {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--teal);
    display: block;
    font-weight: 300;
}


p {
  animation-duration: 3s;
  animation-name: slide-in;
}
p span {
  display: inline-block;
  animation-duration: 3s;
  animation-name: grow-shrink;
}

.btn-div {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    gap: 2rem;
    animation-duration: 3s;
    animation-name: slide-in;
}

#intro h2 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--cream);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    line-height: 1.5;
    animation: shrink-grow;
    animation-duration: 3s;
}

@keyframes delay-bg {
    25%,
    75% {
        background-color: var(--dkblue);
        border: var(--aqua) solid 2px;
    }

    50% {
        background-color: var(--black);
    }
}

@keyframes shrink-grow {
    25%,
    75% {
        scale: 200%;
    }

    50% {
        scale: 100%;
    }
}
#intro h3 {
    padding-top: 10px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.intro-one {
    border: var(--cream) solid 2px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    padding: 2rem 4rem;
    /* background-color: var(--herobg); */
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    animation: delay-bg;
    animation-duration: 3s;
}
.intro-one:hover {
    border: var(--aqua) solid 2px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    padding: 2rem 4rem;
    background-color: var(--dkblue);
    box-shadow: var(--aqua) 2px 2px 10px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.intro-two {
    border: var(--cream) solid 2px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    padding: 2rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
}
.intro-two:hover {
    border: var(--aqua) solid 2px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    padding: 2rem 2rem;
    background-color: var(--dkblue);
    box-shadow: var(--aqua) 2px 2px 1rem;
    text-align: center;
}
.intro-two h3 {
    padding-bottom: 8px;
}
.site-pages {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 1rem;
}

.intro-three {
    border: var(--cream) solid 2px;
    border-radius: 25px;
